Utilities:

To get limit of specific resource and remaining requests of that one:
URL:
	https://api.twitter.com/1.1/application/rate_limit_status.json
Method:
	GET
Params:
	reaources: <resource name> (search, users ...)
Headers:
	Authorization: Bearer <token>
	

To get state's id by name:
URL:
	https://api.twitter.com/1.1/geo/search.json
Method:
	GET
Headers:
	Authorization: Bearer <token>
Params:
	query: <state name>

Twitter error codes:
	Link: https://dev.twitter.com/overview/api/response-codes